    <PES_setting_negotiationIntro>以下的所有概率都只是一个基础值。每一种谈判方式的最终概率按如下方式计算: \n如果产生的是正面结果: P = Base * NA\n如果产生的是负面结果: P = Base * (1 / NA); P = Base / 2 (如果NA等于零)\n同时P会被约束到[0, 1]</PES_setting_negotiationIntro>
    <!-- <PES_setting_negotiationIntro>All of the following probabilities are only base values. The final probablities for each to happen is based on this formula: \nFor positive outcome: P = Base * NA\nFor negative outcome: P = Base * (1 / NA); P = Base / 2 (if NA is zero)\nAnd P will be clamped to [0, 1]</PES_setting_negotiationIntro> -->
    <PES_setting_negotiationTip>Base = 概率基础值\nNA是小人的外交力，和小人的社交技能有关，具体的值可以在游戏中小人的详细属性面板中查看。对于一个正常健康的小人，社交1级时外交力是40%，20级是190% </PES_setting_negotiationTip>

